ager","2. Contacts Location":"Colne, England, UK","Website":"https://elht.nhs.uk/","Org. LinkedIn":"https://www.linkedin.com/company/east-lancashire-hospitals-nhs-trust/"}},{"campaign_name":"NHS Trust - Contacts","source_file":"NHS Trust - Contacts - Last view used.xlsx","source_sheet":"NHS Trust - Contacts","source_row":25,"payload":{"Organisation Name":"East Cheshire NHS Trust","Company Description":"East Cheshire NHS Trust is a smaller, predominantly rural trust covering Macclesfield and surrounding areas. Against EMSOL''s ICP it ranks low for a few reasons - it''s not urban, not a large acute multi-site trust, and is unlikely to have the same loading bay and supply chain volume that makes GSTT, Hampshire or Mid and South Essex such strong fits. The playbook flags rural NHS trusts as deprioritised specifically, and East Cheshire fits that profile.","Account Priority":"Low","Prospecting":"Out Of Scope","(Primary) 1. Contact First Name":"Rachel","(Primary) 1. Contact  Last Name":"Sharp","(Primary) 1. Contact Title":"Asset and Sustainability Manager","(Primary) 1. Personal LinkedIn":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/rachel-sharp-02089a80/","(Primary) 1. Direct Dial - Mobile":"447515992797","(Primary) Contacts Location":"Cheshire, England, UK","Website":"https://www.eastcheshire.nhs.uk/","Org. LinkedIn":"https://www.linkedin.com/company/east-cheshire-nhs-trust/"}},{"campaign_name":"NHS Trust - Contacts","source_file":"NHS Trust - Contacts - Last view used.xlsx","source_sheet":"NHS Trust - Contacts","source_row":26,"payload":{"Organisation Name":"Devon Partnership NHS Trust","Company Description":"Summary: Brief call with Collette. Trust confirmed as low fit - site footprint and operational activity does not align with EMSOL''s core use case. No loading bay or contractor activity of meaningful scale. Not interested in progressing.","Account Priority":"None","Prospecting":"Out Of Scope","(Primary) 1. Contact First Name":"Colette","(Primary) 1. Contact  Last Name":"Germon","